title: On The Nature of Reality with Mercury
description:
This week my guest is my friend Mercury, from the @Sorting Myself Out channel. We discuss the topic of reality, and speak about his unique perspective of the world through his bipolar lens. He tells me of his journey towards acceptance, from seeing it as a curse, to seeing it as a powerful gift to be respected.

watch the podcast version here: https://anchor.fm/podcast-9b57fe4/episodes/On-The-Nature-of-Reality-ef34sv

Mercury’s channel: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC2i_hx_UfauBFh5DA3YWfDg

Follow me on twitter @AndreaLynnlewis
Email me at andreawiththebangs@gmail.com
